# Project 11 — Image Classification (CNN, CIFAR-10)

## Project Overview
This project demonstrates **image classification using a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN)** trained on the **CIFAR-10 dataset**.  
The model can classify **10 classes of objects**: airplane, automobile, bird, cat, deer, dog, frog, horse, ship, truck.

